text: Personâ€™s Name or Website Name Find David Zaas First post: 2/15/2017 Latest post: 2/16/2017 On February 14th, our lives were changed with the diagnosis of Acute Leukemia. As we prepare to fight this cancer, we truly appreciate the huge amount of support we have received from so many of our family, friends, and colleagues. We will be using this website to both update all of our friends and family on recent events, but it will also help us cope with the stress and challenges we know are coming. We appreciate your support and words of hope and encouragement. Thank you for visiting. Read More
